{"tid":1406293,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.5三罷]黃大仙發夢集中討論區","createTime":"2019-08-04T12:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T02:50:43.000Z","uid":26445,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b59cde3d97919d3145fea948c10582df60d22b4b","tid":1406293,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃大仙顯靈</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fnCqMtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfnCqMtn.jpg&h=ae8fe2da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你地準備好射波未?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSihCyo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSihCyo.png&h=f21bd3f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsFAp5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwsFAp5.png&h=3db888be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住我地5大訴求<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 撤回《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n2. 撤回 6.12 暴動定性<br />\n3. 撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會，調查警察濫暴濫權、追究警察開槍責任及元朗警黑勾結<br />\n5. 全面落實雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有！唔好唔記得8月3日夜晚班警犬同佢地啲家屬對黃大仙街坊做過啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDQzEPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDQzEPS.jpg&h=d7c02a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GEEkAoc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGEEkAoc.png&h=db069760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8月5日你地實唔會有覺好瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Metxrv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMetxrv6.jpg&h=e12be602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住！<br />\n<br />\n時間：8月5日下午1點（有早冇遲，你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n地點：黃大仙中間（個心字我唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"04099a5cf573595da42827ddf6b7c052f3a27a1a","tid":1406293,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"05516d6112aa4ceb5eef83fcd93c0c836c605a38","tid":1406293,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該入一入黎幫手推post</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCc3YftZ.png&h=73d6d6c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfS7Za.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfS7Za.png&h=2961d9b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28eda0e6758cb3bd3c1192a66b9c5c3509c83632","tid":1406293,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"街坊準備定大量水 口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f932850da3538c502c5d8e3e6648f31f4e58f1a5","tid":1406293,"uid"